\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af11\langfe2052\dbch\af12\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\fs24\lang3081\sb100\sa100{\cf1\i0\ul\ulc0\b0\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f6
The Church, the purpose of the ages}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
\line }{\cf1\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f6
In the purpose of the Father's heart in eternity past, was the Church.}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
\line }{\cf1\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f6
We are told in Eph 1: 4 - }{\cf1\i\ulnone\ulc0\b0\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f6
... He chose us in Him before the foundation of the world...}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
\line }{\cf1\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f6
